{"tid":582331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女老師の特別授業　第一堂課就和富商子做愛","createTime":"2018-03-06T05:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T15:10:00.000Z","uid":122,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0677c18b2849071d20823a2ed06d2155d4fb36fd","tid":582331,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"女老師の特別授業　第一堂課就和富商子做愛<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯一名35歲女老師妮坎卓娃(Natalya Nikandrova)，日前在為一名富商的15歲兒子上第一堂家教課時，就祭出「特別授業」，直接和少年做愛，更被少年的媽媽撞見。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這名少年杜柯夫(Kostya Dyukov)的父親，是當地赫赫有名的石油大亨，但是父母嫌自己的兒子不學好，在社交網站上常常PO出正妹圖和名車照，於是父母決定，要找全聖彼得堡最好的老師來調教他。最後杜柯夫的母親找到了妮坎卓娃，而妮坎卓娃同時也是這名母親的好友。<br />\n<br />\n就在妮坎卓娃為杜柯夫上第一堂課，妮坎卓娃就祭出「特別授業」，直接對杜柯夫傳授「性愛課」，兩人就利用上課時間直接做愛。隨後母親進屋查看，就看到這驚人的一幕。妮坎卓娃目前已遭到逮捕，恐面臨4年徒刑。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180306/1308933/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180306%2F1308933%2F&d=YJGkDyvkR4pa3We%2BlnO0ki7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0a6e1874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180306%2F1308933%2F&h=93b2495e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180306/1308933/</a>"},{"pid":"799f39a3895cc9c3adde4ba15d0c5c2ced33cf7b","tid":582331,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"快點快點快點......."},{"pid":"de5fb39d623f6f658f44b5b6d25b00b43ba730a2","tid":582331,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"成個夏惠咁<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"e725b5495d2e84e26b6fe29b9e6463798fff0641","tid":582331,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"入邊有圖"},{"pid":"e83f72a95f31a69b447fc0225d4cc151c734bc0d","tid":582331,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799f39a3895cc9c3adde4b